page.title: 15The Garage
page.content: Mr Watson works at the garage. There used to be a bicycle shop there.Mr Snelling owned the bicycle shop.Mr Snelling still lives there.They have one petrol tank.Mainly the same people come everyday.Mrs Taylor owns the garage.Mr Watson is Mrs Taylor's cousin.Mr Watson has been working there for 36 years.They work all week.They have a delivery of petrol every Friday.They fixed their first car in 1910.Mr. Watson does welding, fixes motor bikes, repairs locks and mopeds.It is just him who works there.
